</div>
                        
                        <p>Jacobs noted that although&nbsp;many of the&nbsp;project's prospects look promising thus far, moving the light rail forward will require continued diligence.</p>
<p>“It’s exciting&mdash;it’s something that we just have to keep working on,” she said.</p>

